metadata.name: The Everyones - Steve Miller
metadata.description:
These custom-made characters were created based on trait selections by members of the House of First community who collected 20 or more NFTs from The Everyones collection by Ian Murray. The members were also able to name the characters and received a signed physical as an additional bonus.

There's a warmth and quirky nostalgia about these one-of-a kind characters that makes them feel like your best friends.
